name: 1960's Egyptian Head Clip On Studs

Long delicate gold plated brass chain with a little vintage coin pendant and semi precious turquoise nugget stone.

A one off piece that is perfect for everyday, whether alone or layered.

A one off hand made piece that will add interest to your Winter look!
